vlc:

File->Adv File Open
File tab:
screen:// :screen-fps=5 :dshow-fps=29.9001 :nooverlay
(or :dsow-fps=35 to slow down)
Check Streaming/Saving
Click Settings
Fill in filename (/w .flv)
Encapsulation: mp4
Video:
  type: h264
  bitrate: 512
  scale: 0.75
 Go

 Alternatives:
 http://www.screencast-o-matic.com/
 jingproject.com
 http://danicsoft.com/software/copernicus/
